<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v7" title="Proporcionalidad directa en reparto de dinero" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Laura y Nicolás compran códigos de un videojuego en oferta para revender a sus amigos. La situación se presenta en el siguiente registro:<br />
      - Costo total de los códigos: $<m:math><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
      - Aporte de Laura: $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
      - Aporte de Nicolás: el resto.<br />
      - Cantidad de códigos comprados: <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
      - Precio de venta de cada código: $<m:math><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:math>.<br />
      Venden todos los códigos y acuerdan que repartirán el dinero obtenido de forma proporcional a lo que aportó cada uno.
    </p>
    <p>
      ¿Cuánto dinero recibe Laura después de vender todos los códigos?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        $<m:math><m:mn>37&#160;500</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El dinero total obtenido es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Laura aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del total, así que debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, <m:math><m:mn>37&#160;500</m:mn></m:math> no corresponde.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        $<m:math><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Nicolás aporta el resto: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces Laura aporta el doble que Nicolás, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. El total vendido es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que Laura recibe <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por eso, <m:math><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> no satisface el reparto proporcional.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        $<m:math><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El total de la venta es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Laura aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del dinero invertido, por lo tanto recibe <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> es solo el aporte inicial de Laura, pero el problema pide cuánto recibe después de vender todos los códigos. La venta total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como Laura aportó <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del total invertido, debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso del reparto proporcional</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Determinar cuánto aportó Nicolás</strong></p>
            <p>El costo total de los códigos es $<m:math><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> y Laura aportó $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces, Nicolás aportó el resto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>15&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el dinero total obtenido en la venta</strong></p>
            <p>Se compraron <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> códigos y cada uno se vendió a $<m:math><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, el dinero total recaudado es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Establecer la proporción de aporte</strong></p>
            <p>Laura aportó $<m:math><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> de un total de $<m:math><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Su fracción del total invertido es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>30&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>45&#160;000</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Esto significa que Laura debe recibir <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> del dinero total obtenido.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Calcular cuánto recibe Laura</strong></p>
            <p>Aplicamos la proporción al total de la venta:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>75&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Laura recibe $<m:math><m:mn>50&#160;000</m:mn></m:math> después de vender todos los códigos.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>